dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Sauk County, WI 2025
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Sauk County, Wisconsin in 2025 and includes the layers 'SAUK_ROADS_2025' and 'SAUK_ROW_2025'. [Roads: This feature class contains detailed line work supporting Sauk Counties road network and contains street name, classification, and address range attributes. ROW: The primary division of a simultaneous conveyance and generally referred to as lots, units, or common elements.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
